Package com.box.androidlib.ResponseParsers

This package contains response parsers that consume the Box API response XML and convert them into Box DAO objects.

          Description

Class Summary
AccountTreeResponseParser Response parser for get_account_tree API request.
CommentResponseParser Parser for a comment response from Box API.
CommentsResponseParser Parser for a response from Box API containing a list of comments.
DefaultResponseParser Base response parser for Box API response XML.
FileResponseParser Parser for a BoxAPI response containing a single Box file object.
FolderResponseParser Parser for a Box API response containing a single Box Folder.
PublicShareResponseParser Parser for a Box API response for the public_share action.
SearchResponseParser Parser for a Box API response for the search action.
TagsResponseParser Parser for a response form Box API containing a list of tags.
TicketResponseParser Parser for Box API response containing a ticket.
ToggleFolderEmailResponseParser Parser for Box API response for toggle_folder_email action.
UpdatesResponseParser Parser for Box API response containing a list of updates.
UserResponseParser Parser for a Box API response containing a user.
VersionsResponseParser Parser for a Box API response containing a list of versions.
 

Package com.box.androidlib.ResponseParsers Description

This package contains response parsers that consume the Box API response XML and convert them into Box DAO objects.
